metadata.name: .savium.
metadata.description:
…and I don't know what to do with a kiss 
if you don't feel what I feel, 
and I approach to seek the warmth of your skin. 
I caress your painted moods between the folds, 
I slide almost as if I want to enter your soul, 
I feel you breathing slowly and even if I don't look, 
I know your eyes are closed 
and you look at my heart.
